et\n| note1          = {{lang|ko|\ub178\uc744}}\n| lyrics1        = Park Woo-sang\n| music1         = Park Woo-sang\n| extra1         = [[Davichi]]\n| length1        = 3:37\n| title2         = Sunset\n| note2          = Inst.\n| music2         = Park Woo-sang\n| length2        = 3:37\n| total_length   = 7:14\n}}\n\n;Part 4\n{{tracklist\n| headline       = Released on {{start date|2020|01|12}}\n| extra_column   = Artist\n| title1         = Here I Am Again\n| note1          = {{lang|ko|\ub2e4\uc2dc \ub09c, \uc5ec\uae30}}\n| lyrics1        = {{hlist|Nam Hye-seung|Surf Green}}\n| music1         = {{hlist|Nam Hye-seung|Surf Green}}\n| extra1         = [[Baek Ye-rin]]\n| length1        = 3:55\n| title2         = Here I Am Again\n| note2          = Inst.\n| music2         = {{hlist|Nam Hye-seung|Surf Green}}\n| length2        = 3:55\n| total_length   = 7:50\n}}\n\n;Part 5\n{{tracklist\n| headline       = Released on {{start date|2020|01|19}}\n| extra_column   = Artist\n| title1         = Someday\n| note1          = {{lang|ko|\uc5b4\ub5a4 \ub0a0\uc5d4}}\n| lyrics1        = Kim Ho-kyung\n| music1         = 1601\n| extra1         = [[Kim Jae-hwan (singer)|Kim Jae-hwan]]\n| length1        = 4:20\n| title2         = Someday\n| note2          = Inst.\n| music2         = 1601\n| length2        = 4:20\n| total_length   = 8:40\n}}\n\n;Part 6\n{{tracklist\n| headline       = Released on {{start date|2020|01|25}}\n| extra_column   = Artist\n| title1         = Photo of My Mind\n| note1          = {{lang|ko|\ub0b4 \ub9c8\uc74c\uc758 \uc0ac\uc9c4}}\n| lyrics1        = {{hlist|Nam Hye-seung|Kim Kyung-hee}}\n| music1         = {{hlist|Nam Hye-seung|Surf Green}}\n| extra1         = [[Song Ga-in]]\n| length1        = 4:34\n| title2         = Photo of My Mind\n| note2          = Inst.\n| music2         = {{hlist|Nam Hye-seung|Surf Green}}\n| length2        = 4:34\n| total_length   = 9:08\n}}\n\n;Part 7\n{{tracklist\n| headline       = Released on {{start date|2020|01|26}}\n| extra_column   =