2\n| title2         = Let Us Go\n| note2          = inst.\n| music2         = {{hlist|Dong Woo-seok|Yoo Jung-hyun|Jayins}}\n| length2        = 3:42\n| total_length   = 7:24\n}}\n\n{{Hidden end}}\n\n===Chart performance===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:24em;\" | Title\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:2em;\" | Year\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"1\" | Peak<br />positions\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:5em;\" | Remarks\n! rowspan=\"2\" | Ref.\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.5em;font-size:90%;\" | [[Gaon Digital Chart|KOR]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"But It's Destiny\" ({{lang|ko|\uc6b0\uc5f0\uc778 \ub4ef \uc6b4\uba85}}) <small>([[10cm (singer)|10cm]])</small>\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2019\n| 108\n| Part 1\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/online.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=ALL&targetTime=51&hitYear=2019&termGbn=week|title=2019 Week 51 Digital Chart|date=December 15\u201321, 2019|accessdate=December 30, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Flower\" <small>([[Yoon Mi-rae]])</small>\n| 22\n| Part 2\n| <ref name=\"Week 8\">{{cite web|url=http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/online.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=ALL&targetTime=08&hitYear=2020&termGbn=week|title=2020 Week 8 Digital Chart|date=February 16\u201322, 2020|accessdate=February 27, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Sunset\" ({{lang|ko|\ub178\uc744}}) <small>([[Davichi]])</small>\n| rowspan=\"8\" | 2020\n| 47\n| Part 3\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/online.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=ALL&targetTime=01&hitYear=2020&termGbn=week|title=2020 Week 1 Digital Chart|date=December 29, 2019 \u2013 January 4, 2020|accessdate=January 9, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Here I Am Again\" ({{lang|ko|\ub2e4\uc2dc \ub09c, \uc5ec\uae30}}) <small>([[Baek Ye-rin]])</small>\n| 4\n| Part 4\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/online.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=ALL&targetTime=03&hitYear=2020&termGbn=week|title=2020 Week 3 Digital Chart|date=January 12\u201318, 2020|accessdate=January 23, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Someday\" ({{lang|ko|\uc5b4\ub5a4 \ub0a0\uc5d4}}) <small>([[Kim Jae-hwan (singer)|Kim Jae-hwan]])</small>\n| 18\n| Part 5\n| <ref name=\"Week 8\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Photo of My Mind\" ({{lang|ko|\ub0b4 \ub9c8\uc74c\uc758 \uc0ac\uc9c4}}) <small>([[Song Ga-in]])</small>\n| 35\n| Part 6\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/online.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=ALL&targetTime=05&hitYear=2020&termGbn=week|title=2020 Week 5 Digital Chart|website=Gaon Chart|language=ko|accessdate=February 7, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"The Hill of Yearning\" ({{lang|ko|\uadf8\ub9ac\uc6c0\uc758 \uc5b8\ub355}}) <small>(April 2)</small>\n| 187\n| Part 7\n| <ref name=week7gaon>{{cite web|url=http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/online.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=ALL&targetTime=07&hitYear=2020&termGbn=week|title=2020 Week 7 Digital Chart|website=Gaon Chart|language=ko|accessdate=February 20, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"All of My Days\" ({{lang|ko|\ub098\uc758 \ubaa8\ub4e0 \ub0a0}}) <small>([[Kim Se-jeong|Sejeong]] ([[Gugudan]]))</small>\n| 50\n| Part 8\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/online.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=ALL&targetTime=06&hitYear=2020&termGbn=week|title=2020 Week 6 Digital Chart|website=Gaon Chart|language=ko|accessdate=February 13, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Let Us Go\" ({{lang|ko|\ub458\ub9cc\uc758 \uc138\uc0c1\uc73c\ub85c \uac00}}) <small>([[Crush (singer)|Crush]])</small>\n| 3\n| Part 10\n| <ref name=week7gaon/>\n|-\n|}\n\n\n==Ratings==\nIn this table, {{color|blue|'''the blue numbers'''}} represent the lowest ratings and {{color|red|'''the red numbers'''}} represent the highest ratings.\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\" | {{abbr|Ep.|Episo